                      class="hidden lg:block"
                    /> integrations with banks, messaging apps, <br
                      class="hidden lg:block"
                    /> e-commerce apps like shopify and more
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex">
                <Image
                  loading="eager"
                  class="sm:w-auto self-start mr-7"
                  src={scalable_r_2}
                  alt="scalable_r_2"
                />
                <div>
                  <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-semibold mb-2">
                    Scalable
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-sm md:text-sm lg:text-base">
                    Interoperable nature allows for effortless <br
                      class="hidden lg:block"
                    /> scalability to accommodate growth and <br
                      class="hidden lg:block"
