              Reason 3:
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[#3E96F4] font-bold md:text-2xl text-xl">
              Easily Customizable / Scalable
            </p>
            <p class="md:text-lg text-sm mt-2">
              The most standout feature of ERPNext is its ability to be
              customized. This feature is important <br
                class="hidden lg:block"
              /> because all businesses have unique processes / requirements. ERPNext’s
              architecture makes it <br class="hidden lg:block" />
              easier to handle large volumes of data of mid size cos.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
   
     

        <!-- reason 4 -->
    
         
        <div class="lg:flex lg:mt-20 md:mt-14 mt-7">
          <div class="basis-1/4"></div>
          <div class="basis-9/12">
            <h3 class="text-[#31393C] font-bold md:text-xl text-lg">
              Reason 4:
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[#3E96F4] font-bold md:text-2xl text-xl">
              User Friendly Interface
            </p>
            <p class="md:text-lg text-sm mt-2">
              Usability is the success defining factor of any ERP
              Implementation. ERPNext is well known for its <br
                class="hidden lg:block"
              /> User-Friendly interface that is easy to navigate.
            </p>
            <Image
              loading="eager"
              src={user_friendly}
              alt="user_friendly"
              class="banner-image w-full md:mt-7 mt-4"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
    
   

        <!-- reason 5 -->
    
        <div class="lg:flex lg:mt-20 md:mt-14 mt-7">
          <div class="basis-9/12">
            <h3 class="text-[#31393C] font-bold md:text-xl text-lg">
              Reason 5:
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[#3E96F4] font-bold md:text-2xl text-xl">
              Integrated CRM & Business Functions
            </p>
            <p class="md:text-lg text-sm mt-2">
              CRM is a vital aspect of any modern business operations. ERPNext
              comes with an <span class="font-bold"
                >integrated <br class="hidden lg:block" /> CRM</span
              > module, allowing you to manage customer interactions, sales leads,
              and customer support, <br class="hidden lg:block" />
              seamlessly within the system. Also it helps in streamlining and managing
              processes such as <br class="hidden lg:block" /> Accounts, Inventory,
              Sales, HR, Payroll.
            </p>
            <Image
              loading="eager"
              src={integrated_crm_r6}
              alt="integrated_crm_r6"
              class="banner-image w-full md:mt-7 mt-4"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      
      

        <!-- reason 6 -->

        <div class="lg:flex lg:mt-20 md:mt-14 mt-7 ">
          <div class="basis-1/4"></div>
          <div class="basis-9/12">
            <h3 class="text-[#31393C] font-bold md:text-xl text-lg">
              Reason 6:
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[#3E96F4] font-bold md:text-2xl text-xl">
              Integration Capabilities
            </p>
            <p class="md:text-lg text-sm mt-2">
              ERPNext provides smooth integration capabilities, allowing you to
              connect with other essential <br class="hidden lg:block" /> tools such
              as e-commerce platforms, payment gateways, and so much more.
            </p>
            <Image
