              Cloud Hosting and Scalability
            </p>
            <p class="md:text-lg text-sm mt-2">
              The parent of ERPNext- Frappe- also provides you with the
              flexibility of Cloud Hosting. Whether <br
                class="hidden lg:block"
              /> you are a small startup or a large enterprise, ERPNext can simply
              accommodate your needs. You <br class="hidden lg:block" />
              can start with a minimal setup and then scale up as your business grows.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
     

        <!-- reason 8  -->
   
        <div class="lg:flex lg:mt-20 md:mt-14 mt-7">
          <div class="basis-1/4"></div>
          <div class="basis-8/12">
            <h3 class="text-[#31393C] font-bold md:text-xl text-lg">
              Reason 8:
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[#3E96F4] font-bold md:text-2xl text-xl">
              Active Community and Local Support
            </p>
            <p class="md:text-lg text-sm mt-2">
              ERPNext has a thriving Global Community of developers, functional
              experts and users, who <br class="hidden lg:block" /> ensure that the
              system is continuously updated and improved, bugs are being addressed,
